		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Balt.</placeName> <date>Aug 4. 1830</date>&#45;</p>
				<p>Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">By our friend <persName>Mr. Peixotto</persName> I avail myself of the opportu<lb/>&#61;nity of saying that in addition to the number of subscribers obtained here<lb/> for the Books your are about publishing I shall be able to increase the<lb/> number to at least 25 of each&#8212;you will therefore consider that quan<lb/>&#61;tity actually engaged.  Please inform when they or either will<lb/> be published&#8212;in the mean time I will endeavor still further<lb/> to promote your interest with them.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">With the remembrances of all our family</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">Yrs truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author"><add>&#63;</add> Cohen</persName></p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><sic><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leesur</addressee></sic></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Philada.</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><persName>Mr. Peixotto</persName></p>
		</body>
